ure of","tg/god-eternal-nature-of"],"."]]],"; neither any man, nor the children of men; neither Adam, your father, whom I created."]],[35,["Behold, I gave unto him that he should be an ",["agent",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Agency","tg/agency"],"."]]]," unto himself; and I gave unto him commandment, but no temporal commandment gave I unto him, for my ",["commandments",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Commandments of God","tg/commandments-of-god"],"."]]]," are ",["spiritual",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Spirituality","tg/spirituality"],"."]]],"; they are not natural nor temporal, neither carnal nor sensual."]],[36,["And it came to pass that Adam, being tempted of the ",["devil",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Devil","tg/devil"],"."]]],"—for, behold, the ",["devil",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 76:25 (25–26)","dc-testament/dc/76.25"],"; ",["Moses 4:1 (1–4)","pgp/moses/4.1"],"."]]]," was before Adam, for he ",["rebelled",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Council in Heaven","tg/council-in-heaven"],"; ",["Rashness","tg/rashness"],"."]]]," against me, saying, Give me thine ",["honor",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Honor","tg/honor"],"."]]],", which is my ",["power",["study-note-ref","e",[["Isa. 14:14","ot/isa/14.14"],"; ",["D&C 76:28 (25–29)","dc-testament/dc/76.28"],"."]]],"; and also a ",["third",["study-note-ref","f",[["Luke 8:30","nt/luke/8.30"],"; ",["Rev. 12:4 (3–4)","nt/rev/12.4"],"; ",["Moses 4:6","pgp/moses/4.6"],"."]]]," part of the ",["hosts",["study-note-ref","g",[["Gen. 2:1","ot/gen/2.1"],"; ",["D&C 38:1","dc-testament/dc/38.1"],"; ",["45:1","dc-testament/dc/45.1"],"; ",["Moses 3:1","pgp/moses/3.1"],"; ",["Abr. 5:1","pgp/abr/5.1"],". ",["TG Man, Antemortal Existence of","tg/man-antemortal-existence-of"],"."]]]," of heaven turned he away from me because of their ",["agency",["study-note-ref","h",[["TG Agency","tg/agency"],"; ",["Initiative","tg/initiative"],"."]]],";"]],[37,["And they were thrust down, and thus came the ",["devil",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Devil","tg/devil"],"."]]]," and his ",["angels",["study-note-ref","b",[["2 Pet. 2:4","nt/2-pet/2.4"],"; ",["Jude 1:6","nt/jude/1.6"],"; ",["Moses 7:26","pgp/moses/7.26"],". ",["TG Angels","tg/angels"],"."]]],";"]],[38,["And, behold, there is a place ",["prepared",["study-note-ref","a",[["Moses 6:29","pgp/moses/6.29"],"."]]]," for them from the beginning, which place is ",["hell",["study-note-ref","b",[["Prov. 9:18","ot/prov/9.18"],"; ",["Alma 12:11","bofm/alma/12.11"],"; ",["D&C 76:84 (84–86)","dc-testament/dc/76.84"],". ",["TG Hell","tg/hell"],"."]]],"."]],[39,["And it must needs be that the ",["devil",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Devil","tg/devil"],"."]]]," should ",["tempt",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Thes. 3:5","nt/1-thes/3.5"],"; ",["Moses 4:4 (3–4)","pgp/moses/4.4"],". ",["TG Opposition","tg/opposition"],"; ",["Temptation","tg/temptation"],"."]]]," the children of men, or they could not be ",["agents",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Agency","tg/agency"],"."]]]," unto themselves; for if they never should have ",["bitter",["study-note-ref","d",[["Moses 6:55","pgp/moses/6.55"],"."]]]," they could not know the sweet—"]],[40,["Wherefore, it came to pass that the devil tempted Adam, and he partook of the forbidden ",["fruit",["study-note-ref","a",[["Gen. 3:6","ot/gen/3.6"],"; ",["Moses 4:12 (7–13)","pgp/moses/4.12"],"."]]]," and ",["transgressed",["study-note-ref","b",[["John 8:34","nt/john/8.34"],". ",["TG Transgress","tg/transgress"],"."]]]," the commandment, wherein he became ",["subject",["study-note-ref","c",[["2 Ne. 10:24","bofm/2-ne/10.24"],"; ",["Mosiah 16:3 (3–5)","bofm/mosiah/16.3"],"; ",["Alma 5:41 (41–42)","bofm/alma/5.41"],"."]]]," to the ",["",53],"will of the devil, because he yielded unto temptation."]],[41,["Wherefore, I, the Lord God, caused that he should be ",["cast out",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Fall of Man","tg/fall-of-man"],"."]]]," from the Garden of ",["Eden",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Eden","tg/eden"],"."]]],", from my presence, because of his transgression, where